{"tid":2518310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警世」鹹濕大狗公","createTime":"2021-05-06T02:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T19:30:45.000Z","uid":219096,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbc88676eeb111be333ba24bc7cd30ec1894145","tid":2518310,"uid":219096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYsxVDFcCvrCbJP7mmxSPQECe9egRiPazjufzGg15sdsD?filename=ds3Ra8F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fds3Ra8F.png&h=bd37ea41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSPJd6UZLDV2JiyQLuSipBMeFfYdmPLj6Y2Kf6LQb3dbZ?filename=wQWGym9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQWGym9.png&h=f9ff74af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以提醒身邊的朋友小心呢一隻狗公，<br />\n雖然比佢呃到出去都好戇鳩同埋好蠢。<br />\n但係有好多無知嘅少女就係咁樣就冇咗清白之身，俾人污辱左都唔敢出聲所以我希望可以大家可以廣傳，等佢出名啲，減少受害者。<br />\n<br />\n識佢嘅朋友可以提供更加多相！<br />\n<br />\n佢個名叫威威，佢今次真係威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a59bbf915fe5fa0c45fa722df95583a43d7c02","tid":2518310,"uid":16061,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"有流出扑嘢片你就放<br />\n無人想睇你啲私怨嘢呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"a43745bde70e380b871f96a7988522e74e9ae5eb","tid":2518310,"uid":219096,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"b3a59bbf915fe5fa0c45fa722df95583a43d7c02","tid":2518310,"uid":16061,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"有流出扑嘢片你就放<br />\n無人想睇你啲私怨嘢呀屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"收到SIR，多謝你寶貴意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdfd06bb64ab5046943a573048c992acfda9c5a","tid":2518310,"uid":199252,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:55:37.000Z","msg":"屌你仲以為193"},{"pid":"1dd17ca57e8882018099a6b3d10fce012a63940e","tid":2518310,"uid":219096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,